import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Grid, Card, CardContent, Typography, Button, Divider } from '@mui/material';
import AddIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Add';
import CalendarTodayIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CalendarToday';
import ChatIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Chat';
import AssistantIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Assistant';
import { motion } from 'framer-motion';

function Dashboard() {
    // All values set to N/A or empty for placeholder removal
    const [todayRun] = useState({ distance: 'N/A', time: 'N/A', pace: 'N/A', calories: 'N/A' });
    const [weeklyProgress] = useState([0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0]);
    const [recommendations] = useState([]);
    return (
        <Box
            sx={{
                minHeight: 'calc(100vh - 64px)',
                background: '#F9F9F9',
                display: 'flex',
                alignItems: 'center',
                justifyContent: 'center',
                py: 6,
                position: 'relative',
                '&::before': {
                    content: '""',
                    position: 'absolute',
                    top: 0,
                    right: 0,
                    bottom: 0,
                    left: 0,
                    background: 'radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%)',
                    pointerEvents: 'none'
                }
            }}
        >
            <Container maxWidth="xl" sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="center" alignItems="center">
                    {/* AI Running Assistant */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={8} sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                        <motion.div initial={{ opacity: 0, y: -20 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }} transition={{ duration: 0.5 }}>
                            <Card sx={{ mb: 4, background: '#FFFFFF', borderRadius: 3, border: '1px solid rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1)', boxShadow: '0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)' }}>
                                <CardContent sx={{ p: 4 }}>
                                    <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 3 }}>
                                        <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 2, color: '#2E2E2E' }}>
                                            <ChatIcon sx={{ color: '#007AFF', fontSize: 40 }} />
                                            AI Running Assistant
                                        </Typography>
                                        <Button variant="contained" startIcon={<AssistantIcon />} sx={{ bgcolor: '#32CD32', color: '#fff', '&:hover': { bgcolor: '#007AFF' }, fontSize: '1rem', px: 3, py: 1.5 }}>
                                            Chat
                                        </Button>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Divider sx={{ my: 3, bgcolor: 'rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1)' }} />
                                    <Box sx={{ bgcolor: '#F9F9F9', borderRadius: 2, p: 2, minHeight: 80, border: '1px solid #E0E6ED', color: '#2E2E2E' }} />
                                </CardContent>
                            </Card>
                        </motion.div>
                    </Grid>
                    {/* Today's Run */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={4} sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                        <motion.div initial={{ opacity: 0, x: 20 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, x: 0 }} transition={{ duration: 0.5, delay: 0.2 }}>
                            <Card sx={{ background: '#FFFFFF', borderRadius: 3, border: '1px solid rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1)', boxShadow: '0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)' }}>
                                <CardContent sx={{ p: 4 }}>
                                    <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#2E2E2E', mb: 2 }}>
                                        Today's Run
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 1 }}>
                                        <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#007AFF', fontWeight: 700 }}>Distance: {todayRun.distance}</Typography>
                                        <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#2E2E2E' }}>Time: {todayRun.time}</Typography>
                                        <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#2E2E2E' }}>Pace: {todayRun.pace}</Typography>
                                        <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#32CD32' }}>Calories: {todayRun.calories}</Typography>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Button variant="contained" fullWidth sx={{ mt: 3, background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #007AFF 0%, #32CD32 100%)', color: '#fff', borderRadius: 2, fontWeight: 600, '&:hover': { background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #32CD32 0%, #007AFF 100%)' } }}>
                                        Log Run
                                    </Button>
                                </CardContent>
                            </Card>
                        </motion.div>
                    </Grid>
                    {/* Weekly Progress */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={8} sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                        <motion.div initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }} transition={{ duration: 0.5, delay: 0.3 }}>
                            <Card sx={{ background: '#FFFFFF', borderRadius: 3, border: '1px solid rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1)', boxShadow: '0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)', mb: 4 }}>
                                <CardContent sx={{ p: 4 }}>
                                    <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#2E2E2E', mb: 2 }}>
                                        Weekly Progress
                                    </Typography>
                                    {/* Placeholder for chart */}
                                    <Box sx={{ height: 120, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'flex-end', gap: 2 }}>
                                        {weeklyProgress.map((km, idx) => (
                                            <Box key={idx} sx={{ width: 24, height: '12px', background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #E0E6ED 0%, #E0E6ED 100%)', borderRadius: 1, transition: 'height 0.3s', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'flex-end', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                                                <Typography variant="caption" sx={{ color: '#B0B0B0', fontWeight: 600 }}>{'N/A'}</Typography>
                                            </Box>
                                        ))}
                                    </Box>
                                    <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#2E2E2E', mt: 2 }}>
                                        Total this week: N/A
                                    </Typography>
                                </CardContent>
                            </Card>
                        </motion.div>
                    </Grid>
                    {/* Personalized Recommendations */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={4} sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                        <motion.div initial={{ opacity: 0, x: 20 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, x: 0 }} transition={{ duration: 0.5, delay: 0.4 }}>
                            <Card sx={{ background: '#FFFFFF', borderRadius: 3, border: '1px solid rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1)', boxShadow: '0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)' }}>
                                <CardContent sx={{ p: 4 }}>
                                    <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#2E2E2E', mb: 2 }}>
                                        Recommendations
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 1 }}>
                                        {recommendations.length === 0 ? (
                                            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#B0B0B0', mb: 1 }}>
                                                No recommendations available.
                                            </Typography>
                                        ) : recommendations.map((rec, idx) => (
                                            <Typography key={idx} variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#007AFF', mb: 1 }}>
                                                {rec}
                                            </Typography>
                                        ))}
                                    </Box>
                                </CardContent>
                            </Card>
                        </motion.div>
                    </Grid>
                    {/* Quick Actions */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                        <motion.div initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }} transition={{ duration: 0.5, delay: 0.5 }}>
                            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2, justifyContent: 'center', mt: 2 }}>
                                <Button variant="contained" startIcon={<AddIcon />} sx={{ background: '#007AFF', color: '#fff', borderRadius: 2, fontWeight: 600, px: 4, py: 1.5, '&:hover': { background: '#32CD32' } }}>
                                    Log Run
                                </Button>
                                <Button variant="contained" startIcon={<CalendarTodayIcon />} sx={{ background: '#32CD32', color: '#fff', borderRadius: 2, fontWeight: 600, px: 4, py: 1.5, '&:hover': { background: '#007AFF' } }}>
                                    View Map
                                </Button>
                                <Button variant="contained" startIcon={<AssistantIcon />} sx={{ background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #007AFF 0%, #32CD32 100%)', color: '#fff', borderRadius: 2, fontWeight: 600, px: 4, py: 1.5, '&:hover': { background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #32CD32 0%, #007AFF 100%)' } }}>
                                    Start AI Plan
                                </Button>
                            </Box>
                        </motion.div>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Container>
        </Box>
    );
}

export default Dashboard;
